Route multiple API services.

```caddyfile
api.example.com {
    handle /users/* {
        reverse_proxy localhost:3001
    }
    handle /orders/* {
        reverse_proxy localhost:3002
    }
    handle /auth/* {
        reverse_proxy localhost:3003
    }
}
```

