The client's IP address.

```caddyfile
log {
    format filter {
        fields {
            request>remote_ip {http.request.remote.host}
        }
    }
}
```

The HTTP status code within an error handler.

```caddyfile
handle_errors {
    respond "{err.status_code}"
}
```

The HTTP status text within an error handler.

```caddyfile
handle_errors {
    respond "{err.status_code} {err.status_text}"
}
```

The host and port of the selected upstream.

```caddyfile
reverse_proxy localhost:3000 {
    header_up Host {upstream_hostport}
}
```

Access environment variables.

```caddyfile
tls {
    dns cloudflare {env.CF_API_TOKEN}
}
```

Forward auth passing original request info and copying response headers.

```caddyfile
forward_auth localhost:9000 {
    uri /auth
    copy_headers Remote-User Remote-Email Remote-Groups
    header_up X-Original-URI {uri}
    header_up X-Original-Method {method}
}
```

