}

documentation.value:
Set limits on request body.

```caddyfile
request_body {
    max_size 10MB
}
```

Copy response headers from a handled request.

```caddyfile
copy_response_headers {
    include Content-Type
}
```

Intercept responses from upstream to modify or handle them.

```caddyfile
intercept {
    @error status 4xx 5xx
    handle_response @error {
        respond "Error: {err.status_code}"
    }
}
```

